                  <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>kamrer</add></roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__friedrich_ebmer_QGW_II_II_3350">Fridreich Ebmer, baid
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">kamrer</roleName> der stat zu
