                        des <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">rats</roleName><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>innemer der
                           statsteur</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__philipp_kraukcher_QGW_II_II_3353">Philipp Kraukker <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>burger</add></roleName><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>innemer der statsteur</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__laurenz_swancz_QGW_II_II_2627">Larenz Swancz,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> hie zu
                        Wienn, diezeit <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">innemer der
                           statsteur</roleName> daselbs</rs>,</rs> ihnen <rs type="fn" role="other">zu <rs type="org" ref="org__wien">der Stadt</rs>
                     <triggerstring n="fn"><add>zu</add> Handen</triggerstring></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><measure>7387 lb 60 dn.</measure>, das die
                     gewondlich <triggerstring n="fn">statsteur</triggerstring> vom phunt 8 dn. das ganz
